Turn your head.

1055
01:18:24,360 --> 01:18:25,880
他交给你们了
He's all yours.

1056
01:19:25,090 --> 01:19:26,900
那是什么玩意  我们准许去那里了吗
What the hell was that? Were we cleared to go in there?

1057
01:19:26,070 --> 01:19:29,370
{\an8}{\pos(186,190)}加州  爱德华兹空军基地

1058
01:19:26,900 --> 01:19:28,120
没有  长官  他们用了人肉盾
No, sir, they were using human shields.

1059
01:19:28,120 --> 01:19:29,240
我们没获得批准
We never got the green light.

1060
01:19:29,240 --> 01:19:30,850
给我接国务院  肯定是他们搞的
Put me through to State. They're going to be all over this.

1061
01:19:30,850 --> 01:19:32,390
调出显示
Get those monitors up!

1062
01:19:32,880 --> 01:19:33,870
发现不明物体
We got a bogey!

1063
01:19:34,190 --> 01:19:36,450
-不是空军  -接通中情局了吗
- Wasn't Air Force! - We got the CIA on the line?

1064
01:19:36,450 --> 01:19:38,580
我接通了兰利  他们还问是不是我们
I've got Langley on the line. They want to know if it's us.

1065
01:19:38,580 --> 01:19:40,210
绝对不是我们  长官
No, it definitely is not us, sir!

1066
01:19:40,210 --> 01:19:41,970
-不是海军  -不是陆战队
- It wasn't Navy. - Wasn't Marines.

1067
01:19:41,980 --> 01:19:44,800
我需要答案  能拿到目标图像吗
I need answers! Can I please get eyes on target?

1068
01:19:44,800 --> 01:19:46,900
-不能  -无法识别
- Negative, negative. - Cannot identify.

1069
01:19:46,900 --> 01:19:49,590
马上把武器研发的罗德中校叫来
Get me Colonel Rhodes from Weapons Development down here now!

1070
01:19:56,380 --> 01:19:57,250
我们查了身份
We ran an ID check

1071
01:19:57,250 --> 01:19:59,270
并交叉对比了所有已知数据库
and cross-referenced with all known databases.

1072
01:19:59,270 --> 01:20:00,080
毫无发现
We have nothing.

1073
01:20:00,080 --> 01:20:02,230
当地有高空监控吗
Any high altitude surveillance in the region?

1074
01:20:02,230 --> 01:20:04,050
当地有空中早期预警和全球鹰
We got an AWAC and a Global Hawk in the area.

1075
01:20:04,050 --> 01:20:05,730
这玩意是突然冒出来的吗
So this thing just appeared out of nowhere?

1076
01:20:05,730 --> 01:20:07,300
怎么会没在雷达上发现
How come it didn't show up on the radar?

1077
01:20:07,300 --> 01:20:09,290
只有很小的雷达截面  长官
Got a minimal radar cross-section, sir.

1078
01:20:09,290 --> 01:20:11,630
-隐形的吗  -不是  长官  它很小
- Is it stealth? - No, sir, it's tiny.

1079
01:20:11,640 --> 01:20:13,690
应该是无人机
We think it's an unmanned aerial vehicle.

1080
01:20:14,000 --> 01:20:15,800
中校  这是什么情况
Colonel, what are we dealing with here?

1081
01:20:18,440 --> 01:20:20,930
-我去打个电话  -中士  清条线路
- Let me make a call. - Sergeant, clear a hole.

1082
01:20:25,010 --> 01:20:26,830
-喂  -托尼
- Hello? - Tony?

1083
01:20:26,830 --> 01:20:28,720
-谁啊  -罗德
- Who's this? - It's Rhodes.

1084
01:20:28,840 --> 01:20:30,980
-抱歉  谁  -我说是罗德
- Sorry, hello? - I said it's Rhodes.

1085
01:20:30,990 --> 01:20:33,700
-请大点声  -那是什么噪音
- Speak up, please. - What in the hell is that noise?

1086
01:20:33,900 --> 01:20:35,570
嗯  我敞篷开车呢
Oh, yeah, I'm driving with the top down.

1087
01:20:35,640 --> 01:20:37,460
我现在需要你帮忙
Yeah, well, I need your help right now.

1088
01:20:37,460 --> 01:20:38,820
天道好轮回啊
It's funny how that works, huh?

1089
01:20:38,820 --> 01:20:39,920
是啊  是这样
Yeah. Speaking of funny,

1090
01:20:39,920 --> 01:20:42,270
有个武器站刚被炸毁了
we've got a weapons depot that was just blown up

1091
01:20:42,270 --> 01:20:44,110
离你当初被囚的地方只有几公里
a few clicks from where you were being held captive.

1092
01:20:44,110 --> 01:20:45,880
那里挺危险的
Well, that's a hot spot.

1093
01:20:45,880 --> 01:20:48,320
似乎是有人插手替你完成了工作  是吧
Sounds like someone stepped in and did your job for you, huh?

1094
01:20:48,320 --> 01:20:49,580
你为什么气喘吁吁的  托尼
Why do you sound out of breath, Tony?

1095
01:20:49,580 --> 01:20:50,830
我没有  我在峡谷里慢跑呢
I'm not, I was justjogging in the canyon.

1096
01:20:50,830 --> 01:20:52,730
-你不是在开车吗  -是啊  我开车
- I thought you were driving. - Right, I was driving

1097
01:20:52,730 --> 01:20:54,530
到了峡谷  然后去慢跑
to the canyon, where I'm going to jog.

1098
01:20:54,530 --> 01:20:55,730
你在那一带真没有什么
You sure you don't have any tech

1099
01:20:55,730 --> 01:20:57,110
我应该知道的东西吗
in that area I should know about?

1100
01:20:57,120 --> 01:20:58,740
-没有  -发现不明物体了
- Nope! - Bogey spotted!

1101
01:20:58,740 --> 01:21:00,070
鞭子战机  正在前往
Whiplash, come in hot.

1102
01:21:00,070 --> 01:21:01,950
很好  因为我眼前就有个东西
Okay, good, 'cause I'm staring at one right now,

1103
01:21:01,950 --> 01:21:04,000
马上要被炸飞了
and it's about to be blown to kingdom come.

1104
01:21:05,240 --> 01:21:06,480
我该撤了
That's my exit.

1105
01:21:12,000 --> 01:21:13,330
战情室  这里是鞭子一号
Ballroom, this is Whiplash One.

1106
01:21:13,330 --> 01:21:15,030
我看到不明物体了
I've got the bogey in my sights.

1107
01:21:15,600 --> 01:21:17,230
鞭子一号  那是什么玩意
Whiplash One, what is it?

1108
01:21:17,230 --> 01:21:18,610
我不知道
I've got no idea.

1109
01:21:18,610 --> 01:21:21,070
-能进行无线电联络吗  -无反应  长官
- You have radio contact? - Non responsive, sir.

1110
01:21:21,070 --> 01:21:22,700
那你可以交火
Then you are clear to engage.

1111
01:21:23,930 --> 01:21:25,060
{\an8}超音速飞行

1112
01:21:24,190 --> 01:21:25,190
启动
Hit it.

1113
01:21:30,020 --> 01:21:32,410
不明物体刚进入了超音速  我锁定了
That bogey just went supersonic. I got a lock!

1114
01:21:37,000 --> 01:21:39,570
-导弹来袭  -照明弹
- lnbound missile. - Flares!

1115
01:21:42,030 --> 01:21:44,000
等等  不明物体调用了照明弹
Wait a second. Bogey deployed flares!

1116
01:21:58,990 --> 01:22:00,060
展开襟翼
Deploy flaps!

1117
01:22:01,480 --> 01:22:02,410
我去
Holy!

1118
01:22:02,720 --> 01:22:04,280
那玩意从雷达上消失了  长官
That thing just jumped off the radar, sir.

1119
01:22:04,290 --> 01:22:05,930
卫星盯丢了
The sat visual has been lost.

1120
01:22:06,040 --> 01:22:07,790
那绝不是无人机
No way that's a UAV.

1121
01:22:07,850 --> 01:22:08,870
是什么
What is it?

1122
01:22:08,870 --> 01:22:10,300
我什么都看不到
I can't see anything.

1123
01:22:10,580 --> 01:22:12,800
不管是什么  刚刚已经死了
Whatever it was, it just bought the farm.

1124
01:22:13,580 --> 01:22:15,510
不明物体应该已经被处理掉了  长官
I think bogey's been handled, sir.

1125
01:22:25,560 --> 01:22:27,340
-喂  -罗德  是我
- Hello? - Hi, Rhodey, it's me.

1126
01:22:27,340 --> 01:22:29,170
-谁  -抱歉  确实是我
- It's who? - I'm sorry, it is me.

1127
01:22:29,170 --> 01:22:30,510
你问了  你问的那个就是我
You asked. What you were asking about is me.

1128
01:22:30,510 --> 01:22:32,100
瞧  这不是游戏
No, see, this isn't a game.

1129
01:22:32,100 --> 01:22:35,340
你不能把平民装备飞入我的活动战区
You do not send civilian equipment into my active war zone.

1130
01:22:35,340 --> 01:22:37,560
-你懂不懂  -不是一件装备
- You understand that? - This is not a piece of equipment.

1131
01:22:37,560 --> 01:22:40,200
我在里面呢  是件战衣  那是我
I'm in it. It's a suit. It's me!

1132
01:22:40,350 --> 01:22:41,960
罗德  你查到什么了吗
Rhodey, you got anything for me?

1133
01:22:43,830 --> 01:22:46,770
-标记位置  回基地  -收到  战情室
- Mark your position and return to base. - Roger that, Ballroom.

1134
01:22:49,540 --> 01:22:50,610
在你底下
On your belly!

1135
01:22:50,610 --> 01:22:52,710
像是个人
lt looks like a man!

1136
01:22:52,850 --> 01:22:55,410
甩掉他  翻滚
Shake him off! Roll! Roll!

1137
01:23:03,520 --> 01:23:04,970
我被打中了
I'm hit! I'm hit!

1138
01:23:04,970 --> 01:23:06,620
确认  他被击中了
It's confirmed. He has been hit.

1139
01:23:11,220 --> 01:23:12,800
跳伞
Punch out! Punch out!

1140
01:23:19,680 --> 01:23:21,380
鞭子一号坠机
Whiplash One down.

1141
01:23:21,550 --> 01:23:23,200
鞭子二号  看到降落伞了吗
Whiplash Two, do you see a chute?

1142
01:23:23,200 --> 01:23:25,470
没有  没有降落伞
Negative! No chute, no chute!

1143
01:23:31,020 --> 01:23:32,430
我的降落伞卡住了
My chute's jammed!

1144
01:23:38,260 --> 01:23:40,530
长官  我看到不明物体了
Sir, I've got a visual on the bogey.

1145
01:23:40,730 --> 01:23:41,930
鞭子二号  再次出击
Whiplash Two, reengage.

1146
01:23:41,930 --> 01:23:43,750
如果能击落  就击落
If you get a clear shot, you take it.

1147
01:23:45,920 --> 01:23:47,680
少校  我们都不知道那是什么
Major, we don't even know what we're shooting at.

1148
01:23:47,680 --> 01:23:48,340
让猛禽回来
Call off the Raptors.

1149
01:23:48,350 --> 01:23:49,730
那玩意刚在合法禁飞区内
That thing just took out an F- 22

1150
01:23:49,730 --> 01:23:51,180
击落了一架F22
inside a legal no fly zone!

1151
01:23:51,180 --> 01:23:53,870
鞭子二号  如果能击落  就击落
Whiplash Two, if you have a clear shot, take it!

1152
01:23:53,870 --> 01:23:56,330
你又被锁定了  进行躲避操作
You've been reengaged. Execute evasive manoeuvre.

1153
01:23:56,330 --> 01:23:57,260
继续飞
Keep going!

1154
01:24:05,230 --> 01:24:07,290
降落伞打开
Good chute! Good chute!

1155
01:24:14,920 --> 01:24:17,760
-托尼  你还在吗  -谢谢了
- Tony, you still there? - Hey, thanks.

1156
01:24:17,760 --> 01:24:20,370
天呐  你个疯子
Oh, my God, you crazy son of a bitch.

1157
01:24:21,190 --> 01:24:23,160
你欠我架飞机  你知道吧
You owe me a plane. You know that, right?

1158
01:24:24,450 --> 01:24:26,240
严格讲  是他撞了我
Yeah, well, technically, he hit me.

1159
01:24:26,240 --> 01:24:28,210
你要过来看看我在做什么吗
Now are you going to come by and see what I'm working on?

1160
01:24:28,210 --> 01:24:31,360
不要  我知道得越少越好
No, no, no, no, no, no, the less I know, the better.

1161
01:24:31,660 --> 01:24:33,320
我要怎么跟媒体讲
Now, what am I supposed to tell the press?

1162
01:24:33,320 --> 01:24:35,900
演练  一般不都用这套屁话吗
Training exercise. Isn't that the usual BS?

1163
01:24:35,910 --> 01:24:37,360
没那么简单
It's not that simple.

1164
01:24:38,460 --> 01:24:40,370
昨天一架猛禽F22
An unfortunate training exercise

1165
01:24:40,370 --> 01:24:43,480
在演练中不幸发生事故
involving an F-22 Raptor occurred yesterday.

1166
01:24:43,960 --> 01:24:47,220
庆幸的是  飞行员并未受伤
I am pleased to report that the pilot was not injured.

1167
01:24:47,450 --> 01:24:51,200
至于科米拉村庄意料之外的局势反转
As for the unexpected turn of events on the ground in Gulmira,

1168
01:24:51,440 --> 01:24:55,060
是谁或是什么进行了干预  我们尚不清楚
it is still unclear who or what intervened,

1169
01:24:55,060 --> 01:24:56,330
但我可以保证
but I can assure you that

1170
01:24:56,330 --> 01:24:59,300
此事与美国政府无关
the United States government was not involved.

1171
01:25:04,250 --> 01:25:05,950
的确很贴身  先生
It is a tight fit, sir.

1172
01:25:07,130 --> 01:25:09,980
先生  您越是扭动  就会越疼
Sir, the more you struggle, the more this is going to hurt.

1173
01:25:10,080 --> 01:25:11,720
温柔点  这是我第一次
Be gentle. This is my first time.

1174
01:25:12,950 --> 01:25:14,910
我设计它能脱下来的  所以
I designed this to come off, so...

1175
01:25:17,080 --> 01:25:18,410
我真的应该能
I really should be able to...

1176
01:25:19,360 --> 01:25:20,980
请尽量不要动  先生
Please, try not to move, sir.

1177
01:25:22,300 --> 01:25:23,720
怎么回事啊
What's going on here?

1178
01:25:29,140 --> 01:25:29,790
承认吧
Let's face it.

1179
01:25:29,790 --> 01:25:31,840
这不是你撞见我做的最糟糕的事
This is not the worst thing you've caught me doing.

1180
01:25:33,790 --> 01:25:35,350
那是弹孔吗
Are those bullet holes?

1181
01:26:03,170 --> 01:26:04,150
欢迎
Welcome.

1182
01:26:07,720 --> 01:26:09,550
托尼·斯塔克的赠礼
Compliments of Tony Stark.

1183
01:26:10,760 --> 01:26:12,360
如果你当初按计划杀了他
If you'd killed him when you were supposed to,

1184
01:26:12,360 --> 01:26:13,960
也不会把脸烧掉了
you'd still have a face.

1185
01:26:14,460 --> 01:26:16,660
你给我们点小钱杀一位王子
You paid us trinkets to kill a prince.

1186
01:26:16,710 --> 01:26:18,260
带我去看武器
Show me the weapon.

1187
01:26:19,670 --> 01:26:23,270
来吧  让守卫留在外面
Come. Leave your guards outside.

1188
01:26:39,970 --> 01:26:42,180
他的逃脱带来了意外的收获
His escape bore unexpected fruit.

1189
01:26:45,140 --> 01:26:46,990
他就是这么做到的
So this is how he did it.

1190
01:26:47,430 --> 01:26:49,500
这只是首次的粗糙的尝试
This is only a first, crude effort.

1191
01:26:49,960 --> 01:26:52,350
斯塔克已完善了他的设计
Stark has perfected his design.

1192
01:26:52,810 --> 01:26:55,550
他制作了一件死亡杰作
He has made a masterpiece of death.

1193
01:26:55,930 --> 01:26:59,170
有十几件这种战衣的人  能统治亚洲
A man with a dozen of these can rule all of Asia.

1194
01:27:00,810 --> 01:27:02,910
你梦想夺下斯塔克的王位
And you dream of Stark's throne.

1195
01:27:04,920 --> 01:27:06,590
我们有共同的敌人
We have a common enemy.

1196
01:27:11,460 --> 01:27:12,950
如果我们还在合作
If we are still in business,

1197
01:27:15,970 --> 01:27:18,030
我会把设计给你
I will give you these designs

1198
01:27:19,730 --> 01:27:20,790
当做礼物
as a gift.

1199
01:27:22,370 --> 01:27:23,460
作为交换
And in turn,

1200
01:27:25,420 --> 01:27:27,130
希望你能礼尚往来
I hope you'll repay me

1201
01:27:28,350 --> 01:27:30,920
给我钢铁战士
with a gift of iron soldiers.

1202
01:27:41,550 --> 01:27:44,420
这是你唯一会得到的礼物
This is the only gift you shall receive.

1203
01:27:47,490 --> 01:27:48,710
科技
Technology.

1204
01:27:50,740 --> 01:27:53,820
在世界的这一带一直是个致命弱点
It's always been your Achilles' heel in this part of the world.

1205
01:27:55,500 --> 01:27:58,970
别担心  只会持续15分钟
Don't worry. It'll only last for 1 5 minutes.

1206
01:27:59,810 --> 01:28:01,800
这是你最不需要担心的事了
That's the least of your problems.

1207
01:28:07,450 --> 01:28:09,750
把装甲和其余的装箱带走
Crate up the armour and the rest of it.

1208
01:28:11,740 --> 01:28:13,680
好  我们做个了结吧
All right, let's finish up here.

1209
01:28:17,750 --> 01:28:20,710
让方舟反应堆下的16区做好准备
Set up Sector 16 underneath the arc reactor,

1210
01:28:20,710 --> 01:28:22,780
我需要遮蔽这些数据
and I'm going to want this data masked.

1211
01:28:22,780 --> 01:28:24,470
找来我们最好的工程师
Recruit our top engineers.

1212
01:28:24,470 --> 01:28:26,290
马上给我造个原型机
I want a prototype right away.

1213
01:28:35,570 --> 01:28:37,440
你忙吗  可以替我去办件事吗
You busy? You mind if I send you on an errand?

1214
01:28:37,680 --> 01:28:39,720
我需要你去我办公室
I need you to go to my office.

1215
01:28:40,380 --> 01:28:41,580
黑入主机
You're going to hack into the mainframe

1216
01:28:41,590 --> 01:28:43,470
拿到所有最近的运输清单
and you're going to retrieve all the recent shipping manifests.

1217
01:28:43,470 --> 01:28:44,980
这是锁定芯片
This is a lock chip.

1218
01:28:45,640 --> 01:28:46,930
能让你黑进去
This'll get you in.

1219
01:28:47,330 --> 01:28:48,970
大概是在执行文档里
It's probably under Executive Files.

1220
01:28:48,970 --> 01:28:50,800
要不  就是在幽灵驱动上
If not, they put it on a ghost drive,

1221
01:28:50,800 --> 01:28:53,420
那样的话  你就得查找标题数码最小的
